00192 static XED_INLINE xed_uint_t xed_operand_is_memory_addressing_register(xed_operand_enum_t name) {
00193     return  ( name == XED_OPERAND_BASE0 || 
00194               name == XED_OPERAND_INDEX ||

00197               name == XED_OPERAND_SEG1 );
